A High Court jury awarded £40,050 damages to Mark Price, 36, from Nunhead, southeast London, who sued the Metropolitan Police over allegedly racist incidents that caused post-traumatic stress. 

London-born Mr Price, whose family is Jamaican, was accused of being a Nigerian illegal immigrant.
